OL,4,G2345FThe 1970s Diet: Could It Work for
OL,5,     FYou?
OL,6,     GIn this fun social experiment
OL,7,     GJosie Gibson immerses herself in
OL,8,     G70s food, drink and health
OL,9,     Gculture to see if its diet can
OL,10,     Gmake her slimmer, fitter and
OL,11,     Ghealthier.
OL,12,G0045FThe 1970s Diet: Could It Work for
OL,13,     FYou?
